title: ATN: Preseason Week 3 takeaways
itunes:title: ATN: Preseason Week 3 takeaways
description:
A room with some heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- evaluate the "dress rehearsal" performances from Week 3 of the preseason: Just how for real are the Seattle Seahawks and Jaguars quarterback Blake Bortles? Plus, preseason MVP candidates and is Arizona Cardinals wide receiver Larry Fitzgerald back to his very best? Find out.
